* Data Skipping\nFundamentals
** Delta Lake Auto-Collects Stats
***_ Min / max values per column per file
***_ Null counts, record counts
** Query Execution
***_ Check file statistics first
***_ Skip files outside filter range
***_ Only read potentially matching files
** Effectiveness Depends On
***_ How well data is physically organized
***_ Related records in same files = better skipping
** Clustering Improves Skipping
***_ Co-locate related data in same files
***_ Liquid clustering, Z-ordering
@endmindmap
